[[File:Hammer detail.png|left|120px]] A '''hammer''' is a tool used for smithing items on an [[Anvil]], and it is vital to level the [[Smithing]] skill. Hammers can be bought from most [[general store]]s and will never break. A hammer is also used in the [[Construction]] skill when making furniture, and it is required for some minigames.

A hammer is required to access Bandos' stronghold in the [[God Wars Dungeon]]; warhammers are an acceptable substitute.

